sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Usuário
    participant Frontend as Frontend<br/>(React)
    participant tRPC as tRPC Client
    participant API as API Server<br/>(Express + tRPC)
    participant Auth as Middleware<br/>Autenticação
    participant Router as Router<br/>(doctors, medications, etc)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>(Drizzle ORM)

    User->>Frontend: Ação (ex: Listar médicos)
    Frontend->>tRPC: Chama query/mutation
    tRPC->>API: HTTP POST /api/trpc
    API->>Auth: Valida JWT Token
    Auth-->>API: Token válido
    API->>Router: Executa procedimento
    Router->>DB: Query SQL
    DB-->>Router: Retorna dados
    Router-->>API: Retorna resultado
    API-->>tRPC: Resposta JSON
    tRPC-->>Frontend: Dados tipados
    Frontend-->>User: Exibe resultado

    Note over tRPC,API: Type-safe end-to-end<br/>Sem necessidade de gerar schemas
